room_title: Escape room "Escape the Video Store" by Curious Escape Rooms in Boston
room_description: It's 1999. You and your friends are having a movie night and you have to pick the perfect VHS before it gets too late (Mom wants you home by 9 o'clock), when you realize the store is empty and the door is locked. The lights flicker. What's going on? Discover the mystery. And get out before it's too late. You have 60 minutes.
